me.utk.util.function.void_lambda

Interface VoidLambda0

  • Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface VoidLambda0
    Represents a void lambda function which takes no parameters.

    A VoidLambda0 behaves just like a Runnable.

    This is a FunctionalInterface whose functional method is run().

    Version:
    December 10, 2020
    Author:
    Utkarsh Priyam
